.TH  alsavol  1 "27 May 2025"

.SH SYNOPSIS

.PP
alsavol - Change alsa volume with a single slider
.SH DESCRIPTION

.PP
\fBalsavol\fP is a simple ALSA volume control (\(aqsimple\(aq as in a single slider). It works either at the terminal, or using \(aqdialog\(aq apps like zenity, qarma and yad, or using the TCL/Tk \(aqwish\(aq shell. It can also popup an x11 terminal containing itself using urxvt, xterm, mlterm, or st. It can be configured to know which sound-card on the system is relevant, or just to change volume of all cards simultaneously.
